acceptance_criteria: List-family commands support offset pagination and opt-in streaming output with deterministic behavior and unchanged default payloads.
definition_of_ready: Epic pm-qfg8 exists and no active duplicate list-pagination/stream item exists.
order: 2
goal: External audit remediation
objective: Improve list command ergonomics for large datasets
value: Enables robust scripting against large closed-item inventories
impact: Reduces output truncation risk and memory pressure in automation
outcome: Users can paginate and stream list data safely
why_now: External audit identified list-large-output usability gaps
reviewer: maintainer-review
risk: medium
confidence: high
sprint: audit-remediation-2026w14
