environment: Project workspace execution context for List command large-output ergonomics (pm CLI + Node/pnpm toolchain).
repro_steps: run list-closed over large datasets and process via jq
resolution: List discoverability gap is resolved by supporting explicit --status filtering on list/list-all while preserving existing list-* subcommand behavior and active-only defaults when status is omitted.
expected_result: "Users can run pm list --status <value> without unknown-option failures, and list ordering/projection/pagination contracts remain unchanged."
actual_result: pm list --status in_progress now succeeds; linked verification passed via pm test pm-a4z3 --run (97 tests contracts/completion + 75 tests list/integration) with no regressions.
affected_version: 2026.3.12
fixed_version: target-vnext
component: cli-list
regression: false
customer_impact: Improves automation reliability for repositories with many items
