comments[11]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-03T18:07:10.235Z",codex-agent,Feature created after dedup scan for list pagination/stream scope.
  "2026-04-03T18:55:48.992Z",codex-agent,"Feature complete: list family supports --offset pagination and JSON stream mode; full suite and coverage gates now pass with updated docs/contracts."
  "2026-04-05T20:39:56.309Z",codex-agent,Duplicate-check evidence refreshed; reusing canonical list large-output ergonomics lineage for additional automation guidance updates (no duplicate item created).
  "2026-04-05T22:42:41.706Z",codex-agent,"Normalization decision: feature was delivered and verified in linked child evidence; closing to remove stale open state."
  "2026-04-07T18:14:19.429Z",codex-agent,"2026-04-07 scope extension: list help/UX explicitly documents projection mutual exclusivity (--compact/--full/--fields) with valid+invalid example pair to reduce trial/error for agents."
  "2026-04-26T00:31:14.116Z",codex-agent,"Dogfood UX note 2026-04-26: pm list --status in_progress returns unknown_option while list-open/list-in-progress/list-* variants work. Behavior is deterministic but discoverability is lower for users expecting list parity with status filter semantics. Consider aliasing or guidance hint in unknown-option response."
  "2026-04-27T20:09:36.573Z",codex-agent,"Stale-state normalization 2026-04-27: status intentionally remains in_progress. List pagination/stream ergonomics shipped, but residual discoverability follow-up remains from dogfood evidence: improve guidance for users attempting list --status in_progress (list-family alias/help/error remediation path) before closure."
  "2026-04-27T21:06:19.399Z",codex-agent,"Execution start 2026-04-27: reproducing dogfood gap where pm list --status in_progress returned unknown_option while list-open/list-in-progress worked. Implementing compatibility-safe remediation by adding explicit --status filter support on list/list-all paths, preserving default active-only list behavior when --status is omitted."
  "2026-04-27T21:11:51.369Z",codex-agent,"Implementation 2026-04-27: added --status support to list/list-all command surfaces so pm list --status in_progress no longer errors. runList now treats explicit option status as an intentional filter (including terminal statuses) while preserving default active-only behavior when --status is omitted."
  "2026-04-27T21:14:58.717Z",codex-agent,"Verification 2026-04-27: pm test pm-a4z3 --run --progress passed both linked suites (tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts + tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts => 97 tests; tests/unit/list-command.spec.ts + tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts => 75 tests). Manual smoke check pm list --status in_progress --limit 5 now exits 0 and returns in_progress rows."
  "2026-04-27T21:33:12.934Z",codex-agent,"Final handoff 2026-04-27: global gate run after backlog closeout -> pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift --json (warn on legacy resolution backlog: 10 items; history drift hash mismatches: pm-r9ei, pm-vhdc), pm normalize --dry-run --json (rule closed_resolution_backfill count=10), pm context --limit 20 (active_items=0)."
